      <prop type="x-translation-ref">東門之楊.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>東門之楊，其葉牂牂。昏以為期，明星煌煌。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>On the willows at the east gate,
The leaves are very luxuriant.
The evening was the time agreed on,
And the morning star is shining bright.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
